{"tid":210930,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔識得讚一樣嘢","createTime":"2017-04-21T09:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T12:48:38.000Z","uid":23170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4eae3606d92d6ad143a2703e35b9882418c40d5c","tid":210930,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"好似食人地煮嘅嘢咁，好似永遠都從唔到心入面讚出黎咁。唔知係咪自己要求高咁，成日都好似唔會讚得落咁。你要我好假咁讚我其實做到都呃到下人，但係講左出黎又過唔到自己良心。好似人地整完之後，我最多都係講到，幾好食呀，但係要我講到話好好食，成件事我又覺得太假咁。。。"},{"pid":"15ab66d92e16589b1deab53742c1ef9b0f29685f","tid":210930,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27861ee2a2a5f71a994165f3f7f684905c12aea5","tid":210930,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c82a80794f704d8127453ade0f4cdb2f902a86","tid":210930,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"自我中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2cd2101e4ce443fab3cdbd14480a8e8a52b6b5","tid":210930,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自我中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都叫自我中心，請詳述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236369cd9a8b1c3dbecbb4d142e89f64a1616bdd","tid":210930,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，我係唔識讚人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbe45299223f2dc3f59f43ffa94606a667b6df2","tid":210930,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我</blockquote><b